Resource Profile: Vaccine Credential Bundle

Defining URL:http://hl7.org/fhir/us/vaccinecredential/StructureDefinition/vaccine-credential-bundle
Version:0.1.0
Name:VaccineCredentialBundle
Title:Vaccine Credential Bundle
Status:Active as of 2021-01-23T14:10:07-05:00
Definition:

The bundle of resources that represents the clinical content of a digital vaccination record.

Publisher:TBD
Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle

The official URL for this profile is:
